com.gemalto.idp.mobile.otp.dsformatting

Interface DsTransactionData


  • public interface DsTransactionData
    An interface representing the transaction data for DS, in other words the list of primitives with associated values.
    Since:
    4.0

      • add

        DsTransactionData add(MessageDialogPrimitive primitive)
        Put the given primitive at the end of the transaction data.

        This method should only be used for primitives which don't accept input data, otherwise use one of the add methods.

        Parameters:

        this transaction data (for method chaining)
